=====Usage notes=====
*''Thou'' is used with the archaic second-person singular of verbs, which usually ends in ''-est'', as in, for example, "Lovest thou me?" Exceptions (forms without ''s'') include ''[[art#Verb|art]]'' (of ''[[be]]''), ''[[shalt]]'' (of ''[[shall]]'') and ''[[wilt]]'' (of ''[[will#Verb|will]]'').

